# Models Directory

This directory contains TypeScript interfaces and models for the Field Resource Management feature.

## Planned Models

- `technician.model.ts` - Technician, Skill, Certification, Availability interfaces
- `job.model.ts` - Job, Address, ContactInfo, Attachment, JobNote interfaces
- `assignment.model.ts` - Assignment, TechnicianMatch, Conflict interfaces
- `time-entry.model.ts` - TimeEntry, GeoLocation interfaces
- `reporting.model.ts` - DashboardMetrics, UtilizationReport, PerformanceReport, KPI interfaces
- `dtos/` - Data Transfer Objects for API requests
